channel.title: Need help with my jarred client!
channel.description: If someone could help me over skype that would be great. So I added my cache to drop box and go the auto cache download to work. When I use my regular "run" in my client it will download my custom cache and it will work. but when I use my jarred client to try to download the cache it tries to look for a deathlypvpz cache and wont download properly. I tried rejarring it over and over but it keeps doing that even though the regular client is working fine. any suggestions what the problem could be?
